11#include "call/version.h"
12
13namespace webrtc {
14
15// The timestamp is always in UTC.
16const char* const kSourceTimestamp = "WebRTC source stamp 2021-05-19T04:03:01";
17
18void LoadWebRTCVersionInRegister() {
19 // Using volatile to instruct the compiler to not optimize `p` away even
20 // if it looks unused.
21 const char* volatile p = kSourceTimestamp;
22 static_cast<void>(p);
23}
24
25} // namespace webrtc
